Package: ihmp
Title: iHMP Analysis Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Renee", "Oles", , "roles@ucsd.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for analyzing iHMP (Integrative Human Microbiome Project) data,
    including mutation accrual analysis, gene metrics calculation, and species
    filtering. Provides functions for data processing, statistical analysis, and
    visualization of strain-level evolution in the human microbiome.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
